snippet: The Swedish electronic dance music duo Axwell and Ingrosso tasted stardom as two-thirds of Swedish House Mafia. Now they are readying an album for summer.
abstract: DJ duo Axwell and Ingrosso, formerly of trio Swedish House Mafia, embrace their growing popularity as electronic dance music becomes increasingly mainstream.
lead_paragraph: The Swedish electronic dance music duo Axwell and Ingrosso tasted stardom as two-thirds of Swedish House Mafia. Now they are readying an album for summer.

headline.main: The D.J. Maestros Axwell and Ingrosso Aim to Shake the Rafters
headline.print_headline: D.J. Duo Prepares to Shake the Rafters
